Let $M_1$, $M_2$, and $M_3$ be the midpoints of $AP$, $BP$, and $CP$, respectively.
Then as a midline in triangle $PBC$, $M_2 M_3$ is parallel to $BC$, and half the length of $BC$.
[asy]
import geometry;
